              <h2>Vision & Goal </h2>
              <div class="paragraph-wrap">
                <p>Our vision at Published By is to be at the forefront of fashion innovation. Our goal is to merge the processes of the digital age with traditional craftsmanship to create shapes and products that are only possible by combining the best of the past with the possibilities of the future. 
</p>
                <p>Here at Published By every design is born in a digital environment, we use state of the art 3D modelling programs that are mostly applied in high-end CAD-manufacturing and others more commonly found in the entertainment industry. Creating our products in a procedural way allows us to iterate and finalize the 3D shape to the highest degree before 3D printing it in high resolution on our SLA 3D printers.</p>
                <p>Those printed prototypes allow us to discuss the design and function internally with our team as well as with the traditional craftsmen which help us to create the best final product possible. When we have finalized the product and are happy with the shape it is time to 3D print the master used in many different manufacturing processes, which all are fundamental to create our unique products. From vacuum resin casting to injection molding and even lost wax casting, the digital 3D model is essential in helping us bring the designs we imagined to life.Quality & unique design are our goals, we use all means possible in our modern age to achieve them.</p>
              </div>
              
        </div>
