              <h2>Materials & Tools </h2>
              <div class="paragraph-wrap">
                <p>The core of our workflow and the goal that we want to reach is the perfect melding of engineering, or the process of making and the design that we have in mind. A big part of a good design is the material it is made from and the story it can tell. For that reason there is heavy focus on choosing the right materials for the right job from the early stages of a design onward.
</p>
                
                <p>Hand in hand with a digital workflow comes the difficult  task of bringing it into the material world, to achieve that  we work with the newest tools and technologies that the Rapid Prototyping field can offer. After these first steps we take during the creation of a new design, we step into the field of early production  and there we have to walk a very thin line at the forefront of material science, to make possible what few have tried.Together with several Institutes we work on creating new tools and blending new materials which then can be used to bring our unique product to our customers.</p>            
              </div>
              
