                <p>The fashion industry has a clear opportunity to act differently, pursuing profit and growth while also creating new value and deeper wealth for society and therefore for the world economy. Published By is collaborating with top universities globally to show students the potential of fashion design in the digital age through  multi-day workshops focusing on an end-to-end digital pipeline and the opportunities of rapid prototyping. The goal is to teach students how to create digital pipeline whilst minimizing the need for physical samples and wasting raw material. 
